{"word":"Glory","slug":"glory","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Glory</b> God is, to His people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=3&verse=3'>Psa 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=2&verse=5'>Zec 2:5</a><br/> Christ is, to His people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=1'>Isa 60:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=32'>Luk 2:32</a><br/> The gospel ordained to be, to saints<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=2&verse=7'>1Co 2:7</a><br/> Of the gospel exceeds that of the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=3&verse=10'>2Co 3:10</a><br/> The joy of saints is full of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=8'>1Pe 1:8</a><br/> Spiritual:<br/> - Is given by God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=84&verse=11'>Psa 84:11</a> <br/> - Is given by Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=17&verse=22'>Joh 17:22</a> <br/> - Is the work of the Holy Ghost<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=3&verse=18'>2Co 3:18</a> <br/> Eternal:<br/> - Procured by the death of Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=2&verse=10'>Heb 2:10</a> <br/> - Accompanies salvation by Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=2&verse=10'>2Ti 2:10</a> <br/> - Inherited by saints<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=8'>1Sa 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=73&verse=24'>Psa 73:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=3&verse=35'>Pro 3:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=4'>Col 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=5&verse=10'>1Pe 5:10</a> <br/> - Saints called to<br/> <a h